node.title: Australian chairman of selectors too close to Paine to make final call on his future
node.description: George Bailey says he would not make a casting vote if the Australian selectors were divided on Tim Paine's future with the team, given his friendship and business links to the former Australian skipper.

node.title: Bezos gives $US100 million to Obama Foundation
node.description: Jeff Bezos hands a massive donation to former US president Barack Obama's signature leadership project as he steps up his philanthropy efforts, following criticism that he doesn't give enough.
